          <ul class="text-sm text-white/60 space-y-2">
            <li>• Accurate cost estimation</li>
            <li>• Competitive bidding strategies</li>
            <li>• Proposal optimization</li>
            <li>• Pricing strategy development</li>
            <li>• Bid management systems</li>
          </ul>
